name: Experiment Or Die #60
description: Project to create a new collage every day for a year using my years of personal assets. Todays design is a shout out to one of my favorite directors Ridley Scott and a recent show of his named "Raised By Wolves." The show is an incredible futuristic vision of life amongst the cosmos... with living, feeling, flying, weapons of destruction that can vaporize you with a scream. It is an amazing show, but I am a die hard Alien fan and Scott can pretty much do no wrong. Twitter and IG: Nikejerk
